title: 54: OBITCH look back at it!
description:
Happy Anniversary Geoffs! We love you all so much, and to prove it today we’re coming at you with an OBITCHUARY VARIETY SPECIAL EXTRAVAGANZA where we’re looking at back at all of our episodes from the past year and highlighting some of our favorite moments. Here’s to another year of coffin spinners, obituaries, and dumb.ass.criminalllllls! 


SEE US LIVE IN IRVINE ON AUGUST 4TH: https://tinyurl.com/3fvwbsnz



Follow along online: @obitchuarypod on Twitter & Instagram. 


Write to us: obitpod@gmail.com


Spencer Henry & Madison Reyes

PO Box 18149 Long Beach, CA 90807
